  {
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "> > I think the clearSpecificRefinements should actually be an option of the refinementList widget; I don't think we want an extra widget for that.\n> \n> Why not, but it means we'll need to add it to each and every one of the new widgets using facets. Are we sure we want to do this?\n> What if we want to put it in the header of the refinementList ?\n\nAbout this, I would propose to have a `clearRefinements` widget taking an optional `facets` parameter. If not provided, we clear everything, if provided, we clear only the ones specified (usually only one).\n",
